BILLIONTON SYSTE said unconsolidated sales
in March fell 52.80% to NT$18,252,000 from NT$38,671,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  3/2012           3/2011
Sales             18,252           38,671    
YOY%             -52.80%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             50,553           86,817    
YOY%             -41.77% 
=================================================================
 